{"tid":12311,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"如果自願交出高登ac可以換到lihkg帳號可行嗎？","createTime":"2016-11-29T15:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T06:55:30.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13f175b5187f81f74b74fd6c6924372ab0798f72","tid":12311,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"方便本身有高登ac但isp已經用唔到既巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要俾埋密碼lihkg admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlihkg admin又可以係高登做免費宣傳一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然只限仲用到高登ac，lihkg admin login後改密碼然後自爆cap圖，確保無拎個ac做其他用途！咁可以換到一個lihkg帳號，大家同意嗎？"},{"pid":"247e8606013a3cafd55033b870fb380a1e902860","tid":12311,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"成堆sms衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423d340deb66bab28295402244958d8c416c4bd9","tid":12311,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成堆sms衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以係個人資料睇清楚係咪用isp reg先俾囉，你交個email俾admin時已經知你係咪isp啦"},{"pid":"a4f385bada4042f728226c4c0d434fae3226369b","tid":12311,"uid":13510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成堆sms衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b899d6f0ca426a7febf97eba1cc69b14aba7cf02","tid":12311,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成堆sms衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以係個人資料睇清楚係咪用isp reg先俾囉，你交個email俾admin時已經知你係咪isp啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有isp email直接reg咪得<br />\nadmin機械人咩鬼有咁得閒"},{"pid":"6009323a451c1a8ab69322c91cfd346a782244ba","tid":12311,"uid":40427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成堆sms衝入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以係個人資料睇清楚係咪用isp reg先俾囉，你交個email俾admin時已經知你係咪isp啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有isp email直接reg咪得<br />\nadmin機械人咩鬼有咁得閒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢意思係個isp已經無用到果d人<br />\n例如10年前用學校既isp，之後畢業就無得用<br />\n當然你可以話咁大個人要有isp唔難"},{"pid":"b6e3d35f51edeecf22a7f8070ef548b6ce33327f","tid":12311,"uid":32008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7660b77122509f72180cdb9a566adec5476b6e90","tid":12311,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"見到有小學雞起蘋果fb留言話淨係開放isp注冊係自打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n興幸無開放畀小學雞注冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf3b0c2000b7dd15af50f80a71b0737a15693c1","tid":12311,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"如果係舊大專email我覺得可行，自行email 連巴send 埋証明（如畢業証書）"},{"pid":"6a191856a94b17b6b3f089430c1a7794d18940e6","tid":12311,"uid":7375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b6439059b91e57659868de06760fb51b8dbf504","tid":12311,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係舊大專email我覺得可行，自行email 連巴send 埋証明（如畢業証書）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要點證明到本人先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學生証"},{"pid":"f8892a29cf8af8f2674